        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-100 dark:bg-surface-800 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">📋</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-surface-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Syllabus-Based Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400 leading-relaxed">Roadmap priorities are derived from official exam syllabi and topic weightings published by examining bodies (NTA, CBSE, JAMB, WAEC, and others). We update when exam cycles change.</p>
